how to use this project:

1. You need to install visual studio 2012/13, Sql serevr 2012, and from nuget add entity framework to your project.
2. Evoting is main project and others are model libraries.
3. This project has 4 roles.
SuperAdmin- (highest level)  
MainAdmin
AreaAdmin
Basic users

4. I have added snaps for this application,just looking into that you can see what actions they can perform.
5.authentication and authorization is used here and this application is fully secured
6. Run the database backup or if you are already known to entityframework then use code first approach to generate your own database and data.




